This appears to be due to the key "main" being added to a dictionary twice, but there should be no issue in starting up two agents concurrently on the same branch. Please review this behavior to allow agent starts to happen concurrently.

In some occasions I have found this to start two agents on the same issue - **this** should be avoided. I suspect it is due to the ID of the selected issue not changing while the agent is starting, so the "start agent" button is running twice on the same issue. Add tests to ensure that this is prevented.

